{"tid":2315182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫苗開打｜長者VS基本工人 各群組優先接種次序掀爭議","createTime":"2020-12-07T04:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T05:00:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"529fce1b7ff27675f02d4179cd4946bd7db0d5e7","tid":2315182,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"美國本月將開始為民眾接種武漢肺炎疫苗，醫護人員以及護理中心院友幾乎毫無疑問可以首先獲安排接種，但面對初期疫苗數量有限的情況，哪些人應該成為「第二批」接種人士，在美國社會掀起激烈討論。有人認為應該為65歲長者以及長期病患者接種，以減低死亡率救人性命為先；但也有人認為應該率先為「基本工人」接種，盡快讓社會重回正軌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201207/DSVIBYQ3ZRGJBOK57JATF4HMBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201207%2FDSVIBYQ3ZRGJBOK57JATF4HMBE%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTudgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=86e719d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201207%2FDSVIBYQ3ZRGJBOK57JATF4HMBE%2F&h=493fbcce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201207/DSVIBYQ3ZRGJBOK57JATF4HMBE/</a>"},{"pid":"aaf259b11cbb10bcb385597b483616a2034ee076","tid":2315182,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:55:17.000Z","msg":"BLM 班撚樣出黎話要黑人打先未"},{"pid":"fa74e8ecee71aaff46db82a10326c3972098ef29","tid":2315182,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"美國人係疫情入面唯一做得好既事就係開party播毒整死D廢老，以後交稅養少一班廢老<br />\n政府話要幫老人家先，分明係資源錯配救班醫黎都哂藥費既人，好心就掉班老人家去印第安保留區自生自滅啦"}]}